      "content": "hotlines won't change anything. they just give you scripts to say. it doesnt change the fact that my whole life was built around someone who isn't there anymore. everything i do feels like i'm just performing a role for a life that doesn't exist. it's just constant, heavy exhaustion. i'm just so tired of the noise in my head telling me it's never going to get better.",
